OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773497486
OL,3,CTwo 11-year-old boys rescued at train
OL,4,Cstation in national County Lines
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FTwo 11-year-old children have been
OL,8,Fintercepted at Eastbourne railway
OL,9,Fstation as part of a major police
OL,10,Foperation to dismantle "County Lines"
OL,11,Fdrug networks across the country.
OL,13,FThe British Transport Police (BTP)
OL,14,Fconfirmed today that the young boys
OL,15,Fwere found in possession of cannabis
OL,16,Fwhile attempting to board a taxi alone.
OL,18,FOfficers intervened and the pair are
OL,19,Fnow under the protection of formal
OL,20,Fsafeguarding plans.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
