PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773497486
OL,3,CTwo 11-year-old boys rescued at train
OL,4,Cstation in national County Lines
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FThe discovery in Eastbourne was part
OL,8,Fof a week-long "intensification"
OL,9,Fperiod between March 2nd and 8th,
OL,10,Fwhich saw police targeting the rail
OL,11,Fnetworks used by gangs to transport
OL,12,Fdrugs and exploit vulnerable people.
OL,14,FThe rescue at Eastbourne was part of a
OL,15,Fmuch larger operation by British
OL,16,FTransport Police to stop gangs using
OL,17,Fthe railway.
OL,19,FAcross the country, the police
OL,20,Foperation resulted in:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773497486
OL,3,CTwo 11-year-old boys rescued at train
OL,4,Cstation in national County Lines
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FA total of 23 people were identified
OL,8,Ffor safeguarding during the week. This
OL,9,Fincluded "cuckooed" addresses`homes of
OL,10,Fvulnerable people taken over by drug
OL,11,Fdealers`where officers conducted
OL,12,Fwelfare visits.
OL,14,FBTP Superintendent David Udomhiaye
OL,15,Fsaid the force "will not waver" in its
OL,16,Fmission to bring down these lines:
OL,17,F"Six potentially life-changing
OL,18,Finterventions have been made to
OL,19,Fchildren who were at the mercy of
OL,20,Fthese gangs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
