PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773497486
OL,3,CTwo 11-year-old boys rescued at train
OL,4,Cstation in national County Lines
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,F"These results are indicative of the
OL,8,Fwork that we do every day to tackle
OL,9,Fthe menace of drugs gangs who ply
OL,10,Ftheir trade using the rail network."
OL,12,FThe BTP is now urging parents and
OL,13,Fcommuters in East Sussex to
OL,14,Ffamiliarise themselves with the signs
OL,15,Fof exploitation.
OL,17,FGangs often use "clean" skins`children
OL,18,Fwith no criminal record`to move
OL,19,Fproducts, often using taxies or trains
OL,20,Fto avoid detection.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
